{"tid":81864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Seagate宣布關閉中國硬碟工廠、資遣2200名員工","createTime":"2017-01-15T15:24:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-15T16:01:50.000Z","uid":52651,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"99dfaa476a89c6f365f01d2daca66bcddb1e1417","tid":81864,"uid":52651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T15:24:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.techbang.com/posts/48803-after-was-fined-225-million-dollars-by-china-seagate-hard-drive-china-announced-the-closure-of-factories-and-laid-off-2200-employees\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.techbang.com%2Fposts%2F48803-after-was-fined-225-million-dollars-by-china-seagate-hard-drive-china-announced-the-closure-of-factories-and-laid-off-2200-employees&d=OnZiqc9BiKygMwPj5jzPgQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=35eb9f7c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.techbang.com/posts/48803-after-was-fined-225-million-dollars-by-china-seagate-hard-drive-china-announced-the-closure-of-factories-and-laid-off-2200-employees</a><br />\n<br />\nSeagate在今年1/7日，突然宣布將位於中國的蘇州硬碟工廠關閉，工廠的2200名員工全數資遣，並且依照中國的法律發給所有員工兩個月的工資。Seagate對於關廠的說法是「全球戰略調整的一部份」，不過，時間選在中國農曆年前讓2200多名員工頓時失去工作，也造成當地員工的不滿以及抗議。<br />\n<br />\n中國蘇州的硬碟組裝工廠，是Seagate全球最大的硬碟組裝中心。而且，雖然Seagate說整個戰略調整的背景是PC市場的需求不斷降低，硬碟的出貨需求減少，但是事實上蘇州的硬碟組裝工廠整體來說還是盈利的，因此Seagate的這個決定讓很多人大感意外。<br />\n<br />\nSeagate全球的工廠主要設立在泰國以及中國，而在中國有兩座工廠，分別是位於無錫以及蘇州。而蘇州的工廠是2006年Seagate收購了另一家硬碟大廠Maxtor之後，所接手他們的硬碟工廠。這裡主要是Seagate的硬碟組裝、測試工廠，本身並不生產硬碟的零件。"},{"pid":"a9757aeda56b38a09ab29398e0cd8569b9a0d8e7","tid":81864,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T15:26:19.000Z","msg":"hoball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"297aa93b7d29c487065d7af926dc2c38c18e7757","tid":81864,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T15:29:26.000Z","msg":"近日幾乎日日都有post講支那硬碟廠倒閉，其實係咩同一間？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"188542d790a096f90a7a